# Personal Site / Blog Development Guidelines

Auto-generated from all feature plans. Last updated: 2026-03-13

## Active Technologies
- TypeScript 5, Next.js 16.1.6, React 19.2.3, Tailwind CSS 4, Framer Motion, Zod 4, next-mdx-remote 6, gray-matter, rehype-slug, remark-gfm
- `pnpm` scripts for local development, linting, tests, typechecking, and build-time content generation
- Cloudflare Pages Functions for API endpoints and newsletter flows
- File-based content system: locale-scoped site JSON bundles in `content/locales/<locale>/site/*.json`, shared MDX content in `content/writing` and `content/projects`, plus optional locale-specific MDX overrides in `content/locales/<locale>/{writing,projects}`
- Static asset generation via `scripts/` into `public/` for RSS, sitemap, robots, search index, and GitHub contribution data

## Project Structure

```text
content/
  locales/<locale>/site/*.json
  locales/<locale>/{writing,projects}/
  writing/
  projects/
src/
  app/[locale]/
  components/
  lib/
functions/
public/
scripts/
shared/
tests/
e2e/
docs/
```

## Commands

Use `pnpm`, not `npm`.

- `pnpm dev`
- `pnpm lint`
- `pnpm test`
- `pnpm typecheck`
- `pnpm build`
- `pnpm test:e2e`

## Code Style

TypeScript (strict) with Next.js App Router. Follow existing project conventions and keep content/schema changes aligned across locale JSON, MDX loaders, generators, and tests.

