- Added locale-aware app routes under `src/app/[locale]/...` with redirect shells for bare routes
- Moved site copy into locale JSON bundles under `content/locales/<locale>/site/*.json`
- Added locale-aware content loading with fallback from `content/locales/<locale>/{writing,projects}` to shared `content/{writing,projects}`
- Added localized search index outputs under `public/locales/<locale>/search-index.json`
- Expanded tests and generators to cover localized content loading and localized output generation

